description: Retrieves complete information about one delivery destination.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the delivery destination that you want to retrieve.

nested_items.name: deliveryDestination
nested_items.description: A structure containing information about the delivery destination.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of this delivery destination.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) that uniquely identifies this delivery destination.

nested_items.name: deliveryDestinationType
nested_items.description: Displays whether this delivery destination is CloudWatch Logs, Amazon S3, or Firehose.

nested_items.name: outputFormat
nested_items.description: The format of the logs that are sent to this delivery destination.

nested_items.name: deliveryDestinationConfiguration
nested_items.description: A structure that contains the ARN of the Amazon Web Services resource that will receive the logs.

nested_items.name: destinationResourceArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the Amazon Web Services destination that this delivery destination represents. That Amazon Web Services destination can be a log group in CloudWatch Logs, an Amazon S3 bucket, or a delivery stream in Firehose.
